setting

###### setting #####
seed <- 123
set.seed(seed)

# data
alpha_increase_seq_1 <- seq(10, 750, by = 30)
alpha_decrease_seq_1 <- seq(750, 10, by = -30)
alpha_lamb =  c( rep(10,5), alpha_increase_seq_1 + rnorm(alpha_increase_seq_1,10,10), 
                 alpha_decrease_seq_1 + rnorm(alpha_decrease_seq_1,10,10),
                 rep(10,5))
beta_lamb = 0.5
n_obs = 60
# reprot delay
D <- 10;

scoreRange <- c(as.Date("2024-01-29"),as.Date("2024-02-12"), as.Date("2024-02-26"))
# fixed_q_FR
params_fixed_q_FR <- list(
  data = list(
    alpha_lamb = alpha_lamb,  
    beta_lamb  = beta_lamb,
    n_obs       = n_obs,
    date_start = as.Date("2024-01-01"),
    D = D,
    seed       = seed
  ),
  q_model = list(
    method        = "fixed_q",
    method_params = list(q_D = 100, q_lambda = 0.3)
  )
)

fixed_q_FR <- simulateData(params_fixed_q_FR)
# fixed_b_FR
params_fixed_b_FR <-  list(
  data = list(
    alpha_lamb = alpha_lamb,  
    beta_lamb  = beta_lamb,
    n_obs       = n_obs,
    date_start = as.Date("2024-01-01"),
    D = D,
    seed       = seed
  ),
  q_model = list(
    method        = "fixed_b",
    method_params = list(b = 0.4, phi = 0.2)
  )
)

fixed_b_FR <- simulateData(params_fixed_b_FR)
# linear_b_FR
params_linear_b_FR <- list(
  data = list(
    alpha_lamb = alpha_lamb,  
    beta_lamb  = beta_lamb,
    n_obs       = n_obs,
    date_start = as.Date("2024-01-01"),
    D = D,
    seed       = seed
  ),
  q_model = list(
    method        = "linear_b",
    method_params = list(beta0 = -2, beta1 = 0.05, phi_init = 0.2, phi_sigma = 0.05)
  )
)

linear_b_FR <- simulateData(params_linear_b_FR)
# ou_FR
params_ou_b_FR <- list(
  data = list(
    alpha_lamb = alpha_lamb,  
    beta_lamb  = beta_lamb,
    n_obs       = n_obs,
    date_start = as.Date("2024-01-01"),
    D = D,
    seed       = seed
  ),
  q_model = list(
    method        = "ou_b",
    method_params = list(alpha = 0.8, mu = 0.1, b_init = 0.1, b_sigma = 0.1 , phi_init = 0.2, phi_sigma = 0.05)
  )
)

ou_b_FR <- simulateData(params_ou_b_FR)
